UID:s87CBxbFa_b9_vEGcfMKh
SUMMARY:Cardio Sculpt Dance Fitness Class with Seattle Jazzercise
DTSTAMP:20260325T062903Z
DTSTART:20260326T173000Z
DESCRIPTION:Phinney Center\\\, Blue Building\\\, Room 7: Feel lighter\\\, s
	tronger\\\, and happier after 40 minutes of high-intensity\\\, dance-based
